{"tid":2505971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"抗疫羅生門｜印媒：中國停飛貨機阻運醫療物資 內媒：經港已送印800氧氣機","createTime":"2021-04-27T04:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T04:22:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c02c4ae70a99665bb5f8722822c016ce601910cb","tid":2505971,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"全球疫情仍未受控，特別是印度疫情更有惡化迹象，昨天單日新增超過35萬確診，連5天創新高，新增死亡逾2,800人，各國紛紛施以援手。不過，據印媒報道，儘管中國宣稱提供支持與幫助，但中國國營的四川航空公司，卻已將其飛往印度的所有貨運航班暫停15天，已嚴重干擾醫療物資的運送。不過，內媒則指已透過香港將800部氧氣機運往印度德里。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210427/755QQC2TSJB7TBWR4G5SMROF6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210427%2F755QQC2TSJB7TBWR4G5SMROF6E%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B68F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=44428427\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210427%2F755QQC2TSJB7TBWR4G5SMROF6E%2F&h=1bea1798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210427/755QQC2TSJB7TBWR4G5SMROF6E/</a>"}]}